er quarter.", "score": 0.9475027, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.shacknews.com/article/142020/amd-q3-2024-earnings-results", "title": "AMD Q3 2024 earnings results beat revenue expectations on in-line EPS | Shacknews", "content": "AMD\\n\\n1\\n\\nAMD has reported in with its quarterly earnings report for Q3 2024. On the strength of its EPYC server processors and its data center products, the company reported a gross revenue number of $6.8 billion USD, beating analyst expectations. The company is looking at a positive quarter ahead, powered largely by the demand of its upcoming processor lineup.", "score": 0.918838, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.sahmcapital.com/news/content/amd-q2-earnings-preview-microsoft-impact-data-center-guidance-on-watch-analyst-warns-of-substantial-downside-risk-2024-07-29", "title": "AMD Q2 Earnings Preview: Microsoft Impact, Data Center Guidance On Watch, Analyst Warns Of \'Substantial Downside Risk\'", "content": "Shares of semiconductor company Advanced Micro Devices Inc (NASDAQ:AMD) have underperformed other chip peers and the broader market in 2024. Could the trend be reversed when the company reports second-quarter financial results Tuesday after market close.\\n\\nEarnings Estimates: Analysts expect AMD to report second-quarter revenue of $5.72 billion according to data from Benzinga Pro.", "score": 0.7574541, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.benzinga.com/analyst-ratings/analyst-color/24/07/40018437/amd-q2-earnings-preview-microsoft-impact-data-center-guidance-on-watch-analyst-warn", "title": "AMD Q2 Earnings Preview: Microsoft Impact, Data Center Guidance On Watch, Analyst Warns Of \'Substantial D - Benzinga", "content": "Earnings Estimates: Analysts expect AMD to report second-quarter revenue of $5.72 billion, according to data from Benzinga Pro.\\n\\nThe company reported revenue of $5.36 billion in the comparable quarter last year. AMD has beaten analyst revenue estimates in five straight quarters.\\n\\nGuidance from the company calls for second-quarter revenue in a range of $5.4 billion to $6.0 billion.", "score": 0.6737291, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.coinspeaker.com/amd-reports-q3-2023-q4", "title": "AMD Reports Q3 2023 Financial Results, Gives Soft Q4 Guidance - Coinspeaker", "content": "For the third quarter, AMD generated a revenue of $5.8 billion, while the forecast was $5.7 billion, and adjusted earnings per share of $0.70, versus 68 cents expected. Further, AMD reported a gross margin of 47%, operating income of $224 million, net income of $299 million, and diluted earnings per share of $0.18.", "score": 0.43180037, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://news.alphastreet.com/what-to-look-for-when-delta-air-lines-dal-reports-q3-2024-earnings-results", "title": "What to look for when Delta Air Lines (DAL) reports Q3 2024 earnings results - Alphastreet", "content": "## Revenue\\n\\nDelta now expects its total revenue for the third quarter of 2024 to be flat to up 1% year-over-year versus its initial guidance of up 2-4%. The company forecasts total revenue to range between $15.75-15.90 billion on a GAAP basis, and $14.55-14.70 billion on an adjusted basis.", "score": 0.35006633, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.cnbc.com/2022/11/01/amd-earnings-q3-2022.html", "title": "AMD earnings Q3 2022", "content": "Earnings: 67 cents per share, adjusted, vs. 68 cents per share as expected by analysts, according to Refinitiv.\\n Revenue: $5.57 billion, vs. $5.62 billion as expected by analysts, according to Refinitiv.\\n\\nOverall, AMD\'s revenue grew by 29% year over year in the fiscal third quarter, which ended Sept. 24, according to a statement. Net income fell 93% to $66 million, mainly because of AMD\'s $49 billion acquisition in February of Xilinx, a maker of chips called field-programmable gate arrays.", "score": 0.280888, "raw_content": null}, {"url": "https://www.marketscreener.com/quote/stock/ASURE-SOFTWARE-INC-9346/news/Asure-Softwa